text: Mohammad Fahmi Al-Ayyubi (born December 21, 1995) is an Indonesian professional footballer who plays for Liga 1 club Bali United as a winger. ==Career== He made his professional debut in the Liga 1 on April 16, 2017 against PSM Makassar. == Honours == ===Club=== ;Bali United * Liga 1: 2019 ==References== ==External links== * Fahmi Al-Ayyubi at Liga Indonesia * Category:Living people Category:1995 births Category:People from Pasuruan Category:Sportspeople from East Java Category:Indonesian footballers Category:Persela Lamongan players Category:Liga 1 (Indonesia) players Category:Association football forwards Category:Bali United F.C. players
